resources.user_data:
<powershell>
$file = $env:SystemRoot + "\Temp\" + (Get-Date).ToString("MM-dd-yy-hh-mm")
New-Item $file -ItemType file
enable-psremoting -Force
Set-ExecutionPolicy -ExecutionPolicy RemoteSigned -Force
New-NetFirewallRule -DisplayName 'PS Inbound' -Profile @('Domain', 'Private') -Direction Inbound -Action Allow -Protocol TCP -LocalPort @('5985')
</powershell>
